Rulings.Base:
1. Sending a 'Blackwing' monster to the GY is a cost.
2. The effect targets 1 Defense Position monster your opponent controls.
3. "Black-Winged Dragon" and "Black-Winged Strafe" are not 'Blackwing' cards.
4. If the target monster your opponent controls is no longer in Defense Position when the effect of "Black-Winged Strafe" resolves, it is still sent to the GY.
